Python 3.14-64. 
MediaPipe 0.10.32. 

Run by" python config.py "in terminal 
p for pause
j for rewind
l for wind forward
r for reload pose search

Explaination to AI, the videosequences are from handball practices,
where leftwing players are shooting wingshots. The goal is to track the movement
of the attacking player. The will be moving from left to right in the frame and
jump then shoot the ball. No tracking of the ball is needed. 